<li class='cover' id='bookCover_359194'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/359194.The_Lucifer_Effect"><img alt="The Lucifer Effect: Understanding How Good People Turn Evil" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388365513l/359194._SX98_.jpg" />
