o think again and how we can learn to do it as individuals, arguing that \'grit\' alone can actually be counterproductive. Section 2 discusses how we can help others think again through learning about \'argument literacy\'. And the final section 3 looks at how schools, businesses and governments fall short in building cultures that encourage rethinking.\n\nIn the end, learning to rethink may be the secret skill to give you the edge in a world changing faster than ever.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"9119109072829667811\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'18_book_55539565\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"jlSqbm6VSL8aX5XtR/nn74Cz2iQ/Eyy8ABnPr85hVvvlsdE6cCLQNRADhJTOmi1NvUjcQlkeaXEFkCH675mI0Q==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"55539565\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"18_book_55539565\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/11324722-the-righteous-mind\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\n<span class=\'progressTrigger\'>Want to Read<\/sp